'''Gateway''' was the main complex of [[Senate Select Committee for Refugees|SELCORE's]] efforts to lodge displaced refegees on [[Duro/Legends|Duro]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. Constructed upon the ruins of [[Tayana]], the domed structure was located below one of the twenty orbital stations housed in the planet's orbit. Constantly quarreling with [[Settlement 32]], they were bickering over supplies non-stop.

When evacuation orders came down during the [[Battle of Duro (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Duro]], three [[land crawler]]s carrying refugees were destroyed by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]].

